2008-11-08  Luca Bruno  <lethalman88@gmail.com>

	* src/vgl-main-window.c (create_main_menu):
	Use ui_menu_item_create_from_icon
	Reorganize Actions menu items
	(vgl_main_window_toggle_visibility): present() when not is_active()

	* src/vgl-tray-icon.c
	Removed the show_app menu item
	(ctxt_menu_item_create): renamed in uimisc.c
	(ctxt_menu_create):
	Use the new ui_menu_item_create_from_icon

	* src/uimisc.c (ui_menu_item_create_from_icon):
	Added to generalize creating menu items for common actions

