	* src/playlist.h
	* src/controller.c (download_track_thread)
	(download_track_dlwin_cb, controller_download_track): Don't
	download a track if it's already being downloaded.

	* src/dlwin.h
	* src/dlwin.c (dlwin_download_file, dlwin_download_file_thread):
	Now dlwin accepts a callback to call after a download has been
	finished.

2008-10-06  Alberto Garcia  <agarcia@igalia.com>

	* src/vgl-main-window.c (download_track_selected)
	* src/controller.c (controller_download_track)
	(download_track_thread): Allow downloading tracks in background
	without using the download window.
	Fix leak of the LastfmTrack object when downloading a track.

