2008-09-25  Alberto Garcia  <agarcia@igalia.com>

	* src/http.c (http_download_file): Open output file in binary
	mode to avoid problems on non-POSIX systems.

2008-09-09  Alberto Garcia  <agarcia@igalia.com>

	* debian/control: Move Homepage field to the source paragraph.

2008-09-07  Alberto Garcia  <agarcia@igalia.com>

	* scripts/vagalumectl: Hide error message if 'pidof' or 'pgrep'
	don't exist.

2008-09-06  Alberto Garcia  <agarcia@igalia.com>

	New "Stop playback after ..." feature based on the previous "Stop
	after this track" and a patch by Claudio Saavedra to add sleep
	timer support.

	This closes feature request #2377

	* src/controller.h
	* src/controller.c:
	stopping_after_track renamed to stop_after_this_track.
	(stop_after_timeout, controller_set_stop_after):
	Ask the user when to stop, and create a g_timeout if necessary.

	* src/uimisc.h
	* src/uimisc.c
	(stop_after_radio_button_toggled, stop_after_entry_changed)
	(ui_stop_after_dialog, stop_after_dialog_update_sensitivity):
	New dialog to ask the user when to stop playback.

	* src/vgl-main-window.c
	(VglMainWindowPrivate): Don't store the "Stop after..." menu entry
	anymore.
	(vgl_main_window_set_state, stop_after_selected)
	(create_main_menu): Replace the old "Stop after this track" menu
	entry with "Stop after ...", which opens a dialog.

2008-09-05  Alberto Garcia  <agarcia@igalia.com>

	* src/imstatus.c (im_set_status_idle)
	* src/uimisc.c (usercfg_add_imstatus_settings):
	Add {station} keyword to the IM status template.

